<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Employee Directory - Evil Capitalistic Corp</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>ğŸ’¼ Employee Directory</h1>
            <nav>
